### 创建测试租户
POST http://localhost:9090/api/v1/tenants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "certificate_no": "91110000MA00ABCD12",
  "name": "测试租户",
  "type": 1,
  "contact_name": "张三",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "status": 1
}

### 创建测试用户
POST http://localhost:9090/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "phone": "13900139000",
  "password": "password123",
  "status": 1
}

### 测试登录 - 使用用户名
POST http://localhost:9090/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identity": "testuser",
  "password": "password123",
  "tenant_name": "测试租户"
}

### 测试登录 - 使用邮箱
POST http://localhost:9090/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identity": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "tenant_name": "测试租户"
}

### 测试登录 - 使用手机号
POST http://localhost:9090/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identity": "13900139000",
  "password": "password123",
  "tenant_name": "测试租户"
}

### 测试登录 - 使用租户ID
POST http://localhost:9090/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identity": "testuser",
  "password": "password123",
  "tenant_id": "{{tenant_id}}"
}

### 测试获取当前用户信息
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 测试刷新Token
POST http://localhost:9090/api/v1/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 测试退出登录
POST http://localhost:9090/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
